@model string 
 
<div class="govuk-accordion" data-module="govuk-accordion" id="accordion-default">
    <div class="govuk-accordion__section ">
        <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
            <h2 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
                <button type="button" id="accordion-default-heading-1" aria-controls="@Model-accordion-default-content-1" class="govuk-accordion__section-button govuk-!-font-size-19" aria-expanded="false">
                    Assessment criteria
                    <span class="govuk-accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div id="accordion-default-content-1" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-default-heading-1">
            <p class='govuk-body-s'>Factors our assessors will consider include the following:</p>
            <ul class="govuk-body-s govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>is your budget and breakdown realistic?</li>
                <li>does the work you've planned match the predicted spend on the cost breakdown form?</li>
                <li>is there a strong case for public money adding value?</li>
                <li>does your project offer good value for money?</li>
                <li>do the project costs provide fair market value?</li>
                <li>have you made a convincing case for using sub-contractors instead of extra consortium partners? (if relevant)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
        <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
            <h2 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
                <button type="button" id="accordion-default-heading-1a" aria-controls="@Model-accordion-default-content-2" class="govuk-accordion__section-button govuk-!-font-size-19" aria-expanded="false">
                    Public finance limits
                    <span class="govuk-accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div id="accordion-default-content-1a" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-default-heading-1a">
            <p class="govuk-body-s">You can only claim a certain amount of public money towards your eligible project costs. </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">This amount depends on your organisation's size, location and the type of work you're doing.  </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">Any money you claim through BEIS will form part of this total.  </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">Public funding includes money from:  </p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-font-size-16">
                <li>other government departments </li>
                <li>UK public bodies</li>
                <li>other governments or government organisations (From UK or elsewhere)  </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">If you are applying for any other public funding, or are expecting to receive it, you need to tell us in your application.  </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">If you've breached the rules, you'll need to repay any money you've received, including interest.  </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">You can find out how much public money you can claim towards your eligible project costs in question 6.1. </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
        <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
            <h2 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
                <button type="button" id="accordion-default-heading-2" aria-controls="@Model-accordion-default-content-3" class="govuk-accordion__section-button govuk-!-font-size-19" aria-expanded="false">
                    Match funding contributions
                    <span class="govuk-accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div id="accordion-default-content-2" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-default-heading-2">
            <p class="govuk-body-s">Your match funding contribution is the minimum amount you must pay towards your eligible project costs. </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">How much you need to pay depends on several factors.  </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">These include:  </p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-font-size-16">
                <li>the category of aid you're applying for </li>
                <li>your organisation's size </li>
                <li>whether you're applying on your own or as part of consortium  </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">You can find out your match funding contribution in question 6.1.  </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
        <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
            <h2 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
                <button type="button" id="accordion-default-heading-3" aria-controls="@Model-accordion-default-content-4" class="govuk-accordion__section-button govuk-!-font-size-19" aria-expanded="false">
                    Completing the project cost breakdown form
                    <span class="govuk-accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div id="accordion-default-content-3" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-default-heading-3">
            <p class="govuk-body-s">We need you to fill in the project cost breakdown form to assess your application. </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s">You'll be asked to give information about your projects costs. </p>
            <p class="govuk-body-s"> This includes:  </p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-!-font-size-16">
                <li>a breakdown of costs for each partner (if relevant) </li>
                <li>labour and overheads </li>
                <li>materials and equipment you'll need  </li>
                <li>subcontractors   </li>
                <li>travel and subsistence   </li>
                <li>other costs   </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="govuk-body-s"> You can give extra information about your costs in the financial background section (question 6.3).   </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>